## Test 1 — FR-1.1/FR-1.2/FR-1.3/FR-1.4: Tre-tier fuld dækning + invariant

Ref: petition058.feature (AC-1 blandet tre-tier scenario)
GIL § 7, stk. 1, nr. 1–3: Disbursement 10 000 DKK mod tier-1 = 3 000, tier-2 = 5 000,
tier-3 = 4 000 (men kun 2 000 er tilgængeligt). tier1 = 3 000, tier2 = 5 000,
tier3 = 2 000, residual = 0. Invariant: tier1+tier2+tier3+residual = disbursement.

```catala
declaration scope ModregningTest1:
  comp scope ModregningsRaekkefoeigen

scope ModregningTest1:
  # Test: FR-1.1/1.2/1.3/1.4 tre-tier fuld dækning
  # Ref: petition058 AC-1 / ModregningTest1
  definition comp.udbetalingsBeloeb equals 10000.00
  definition comp.tier1FordringerTotal equals 3000.00
  definition comp.tier2FordringerTotal equals 5000.00
  definition comp.tier3FordringerTotal equals 4000.00
  assertion comp.tier1DaekningBeloeb = 3000.00
  assertion comp.tier2DaekningBeloeb = 5000.00
  assertion comp.tier3DaekningBeloeb = 2000.00
  assertion comp.residualUdbetalingBeloeb = 0.00
  assertion comp.restEfterTier1 = 7000.00
  assertion comp.restEfterTier2 = 2000.00
  assertion comp.tier1DaekningBeloeb + comp.tier2DaekningBeloeb +
    comp.tier3DaekningBeloeb + comp.residualUdbetalingBeloeb = 10000.00
```

---

## Test 2 — FR-1.1: Tier-1 udtømmende — ingen tier-2 eller tier-3 dækning

Ref: petition058.feature (AC-2 tier-1 fuld dækning scenario)
GIL § 7, stk. 1, nr. 1: Disbursement 2 000 DKK mod tier-1 = 2 000. tier-1 udtømmer
hele udbetalingsbeløbet; tier-2 og tier-3 modtager intet.

```catala
declaration scope ModregningTest2:
  comp scope ModregningsRaekkefoeigen

scope ModregningTest2:
  # Test: FR-1.1 tier-1 udtømmende — DaekningsRaekkefoeigenService ikke kaldt
  # Ref: petition058 AC-2 / ModregningTest2
  definition comp.udbetalingsBeloeb equals 2000.00
  definition comp.tier1FordringerTotal equals 2000.00
  definition comp.tier2FordringerTotal equals 3000.00
  definition comp.tier3FordringerTotal equals 0.00
  assertion comp.tier1DaekningBeloeb = 2000.00
  assertion comp.tier2DaekningBeloeb = 0.00
  assertion comp.tier3DaekningBeloeb = 0.00
  assertion comp.residualUdbetalingBeloeb = 0.00
  assertion comp.restEfterTier1 = 0.00
```

---

## Test 3 — FR-1.4: Fuld residual udbetaling — ingen aktive fordringer

Ref: petition058.feature (FR-1.4 residualUdbetalingBeloeb)
GIL § 7, stk. 1: Alle tiers er 0 DKK; disbursement returneres fuldt til debitor.

```catala
declaration scope ModregningTest3:
  comp scope ModregningsRaekkefoeigen

scope ModregningTest3:
  # Test: FR-1.4 ingen fordringer → fuldt residual til debitor
  # Ref: petition058 FR-1.4 / ModregningTest3
  definition comp.udbetalingsBeloeb equals 5000.00
  definition comp.tier1FordringerTotal equals 0.00
  definition comp.tier2FordringerTotal equals 0.00
  definition comp.tier3FordringerTotal equals 0.00
  assertion comp.tier1DaekningBeloeb = 0.00
  assertion comp.tier2DaekningBeloeb = 0.00
  assertion comp.tier3DaekningBeloeb = 0.00
  assertion comp.residualUdbetalingBeloeb = 5000.00
```

