## Test 4 — FR-1.2/FR-1.3: Tier-2 fuld, tier-3 delvis dækning

Ref: petition058.feature (tier-3 restdækning scenario)
GIL § 7, stk. 1, nr. 2–3: Disbursement 3 200 DKK, tier-2 = 2 000, tier-3 = 1 800
(kun 1 200 DKK dækkes; 0 DKK residual).

```catala
declaration scope ModregningTest4:
  comp scope ModregningsRaekkefoeigen

scope ModregningTest4:
  # Test: FR-1.2/1.3 tier-2 fuld dækning, tier-3 delvis dækning
  # Ref: petition058.feature tier-3 restdækning / ModregningTest4
  definition comp.udbetalingsBeloeb equals 3200.00
  definition comp.tier1FordringerTotal equals 0.00
  definition comp.tier2FordringerTotal equals 2000.00
  definition comp.tier3FordringerTotal equals 1800.00
  assertion comp.tier1DaekningBeloeb = 0.00
  assertion comp.tier2DaekningBeloeb = 2000.00
  assertion comp.tier3DaekningBeloeb = 1200.00
  assertion comp.residualUdbetalingBeloeb = 0.00
  assertion comp.restEfterTier2 = 1200.00
```

