## Test 14 — FR-4.4: OVERSKYDENDE_SKAT — foersteDagNaesteMaaned < kildeskattelovGraense

Ref: petition058.feature AC-13 (Kildeskattelov § 62 særlig startdato)
Kildeskattelov § 62: indkomstAar=2024 → kildeskattelovGraenseDato = |2025-09-01|.
receiptDate = 2025-04-01 → foersteDagNaesteMaaned = |2025-05-01|.
Siden |2025-05-01| < |2025-09-01| → renteGodtgoerelseStartDato = |2025-09-01| (Kildeskattelov-undtagelse).

```catala
declaration scope ModregningTest14:
  comp scope RenteGodtgoerelseStartDato

scope ModregningTest14:
  # Test: FR-4.4 OVERSKYDENDE_SKAT → kildeskattelovGraenseDato bruges (> foersteDag)
  # Ref: petition058 AC-13 / ModregningTest14
  definition comp.beslutningInden5BankDage equals false
  definition comp.udbetalingType equals OVERSKYDENDE_SKAT
  definition comp.foersteDagNaesteMaaned equals |2025-05-01|
  definition comp.kildeskattelovGraenseDato equals |2025-09-01|
  assertion comp.renteGodtgoerelseStartDato = |2025-09-01|
  assertion comp.ingenRenteGodtgoerelse = false
```

---

## Test 15 — FR-4.4: OVERSKYDENDE_SKAT — foersteDagNaesteMaaned > kildeskattelovGraense

Ref: GIL § 8b + Kildeskattelov § 62 — tilfælde hvor standard-startdato er SENERE end § 62-grænse
Kildeskattelov § 62: kildeskattelovGraenseDato = |2025-09-01|.
receiptDate sent: foersteDagNaesteMaaned = |2025-10-01|.
Siden |2025-10-01| >= |2025-09-01| → renteGodtgoerelseStartDato = |2025-10-01| (standardregel vinder).

```catala
declaration scope ModregningTest15:
  comp scope RenteGodtgoerelseStartDato

scope ModregningTest15:
  # Test: FR-4.4 OVERSKYDENDE_SKAT → foersteDagNaesteMaaned bruges (> kildeskattelovGraenseDato)
  # Ref: Kildeskattelov § 62 — tilfælde hvor foersteDag er sent / ModregningTest15
  definition comp.beslutningInden5BankDage equals false
  definition comp.udbetalingType equals OVERSKYDENDE_SKAT
  definition comp.foersteDagNaesteMaaned equals |2025-10-01|
  definition comp.kildeskattelovGraenseDato equals |2025-09-01|
  assertion comp.renteGodtgoerelseStartDato = |2025-10-01|
  assertion comp.ingenRenteGodtgoerelse = false
```

---

