Ref: petition058 FR-4.2 standardregel
GIL § 8b: ANDRE_TYPER → ingen undtagelse → renteGodtgoerelseStartDato = foersteDagNaesteMaaned.

```catala
declaration scope ModregningTest16:
  comp scope RenteGodtgoerelseStartDato

scope ModregningTest16:
  # Test: FR-4.2 ANDRE_TYPER → foersteDagNaesteMaaned (basisregel)
  # Ref: petition058 FR-4.2 / ModregningTest16
  definition comp.beslutningInden5BankDage equals false
  definition comp.udbetalingType equals ANDRE_TYPER
  definition comp.foersteDagNaesteMaaned equals |2025-05-01|
  definition comp.kildeskattelovGraenseDato equals |2025-09-01|
  assertion comp.renteGodtgoerelseStartDato = |2025-05-01|
  assertion comp.ingenRenteGodtgoerelse = false
```

