## Test 17 — FR-4.3: 5-bankdages-undtagelse → ingenRenteGodtgoerelse = true

Ref: petition058.feature AC-12 (5-banking-day exception)
GIL § 8b: beslutningInden5BankDage = true → ingen rentegodtgørelse.

```catala
declaration scope ModregningTest17:
  comp scope RenteGodtgoerelseStartDato

scope ModregningTest17:
  # Test: FR-4.3 5-bankdages-undtagelse → ingenRenteGodtgoerelse = true
  # Ref: petition058 AC-12 / ModregningTest17
  definition comp.beslutningInden5BankDage equals true
  definition comp.udbetalingType equals ANDRE_TYPER
  definition comp.foersteDagNaesteMaaned equals |2025-04-01|
  definition comp.kildeskattelovGraenseDato equals |2025-09-01|
  assertion comp.ingenRenteGodtgoerelse = true
```

